# Pick A Flick

Neon arcade movie wheel: spin → category → movie → ticket-style result with synced audio.

Static HTML/JS/CSS under `app/` — no app build step. Use `scripts/serve-static.ps1` for local dev (required for fetch/audio).

## Key files

| Path | Role |
|------|------|
| `app/index.html`, `app/main.js`, `app/style.css` | App UI and logic |
| `scripts/` | Metadata, audio, and dev utilities |
| `audio/` | Win clips (`audio/win/<category>/`) and UI clips (`audio/ui/`) |
| `graphics/` | UI artwork (`graphics/ui/`), Tix Mix title cards (`graphics/tix-mix/`) |

## Source of truth vs generated — edit the left, not the right

| Edit this | Generated (do not hand-edit) |
|-----------|-------------------------------|
| `app/main.js` → `movieDatabase` | `app/generated/movie-metadata.js` |
| `app/watched-movies.js` | — |
| `scripts/audio-paths.mjs` | `app/generated/audio-paths.js` |
| `scripts/win-clip-categories.mjs` + clip folders | `app/generated/win-clips-manifest.js` |
| (after clip changes) run refresh | `app/generated/audio-gain-map.js`, `coin-flip-blip-map.js`, `shuffle-golden-ticket-map.js` |

## Category names must match across

`movieDatabase` keys, `scripts/win-clip-categories.mjs`, and `audio/win/<folder>/`.

## Code style

- `app/main.js` is intentionally monolithic (~6,700 lines) — do not split or refactor unless asked.
- Prefer minimal, focused diffs; match existing patterns.
- Draft audio clips: `audio/_staging/` or prefix filenames with `_` in win folders.
- Draft graphics: `graphics/_staging/` or prefix filenames with `_` in `graphics/tix-mix/`.

## npm scripts (common)

- `npm run refresh-audio` — sync paths, manifests, gain maps
- `npm run generate-metadata:ps` — regenerate `app/generated/movie-metadata.js` (needs `.env` / `OMDB_API_KEY`)
- `npm run watch-audio` — auto-refresh on clip changes

